   County Assessor: Mark J. Carrillo Serving since January 1, 1999

                                                                  Overview
   The County Assessor's Office determines the property value of homes,
   businesses, and other taxable property in Bernalillo County. The
   Assessor's Office also prepares the tax roll for the County Treasurer
   on real property (land and improvements); personal property (office
   equipment); livestock and mobile homes.

   Economic Dev.

